{
  "chapter": 69,
  "chapter_summary": "张玉珍从高寿府第奔出，欲追杀高寿。芮玮在窄巷拦截，以化神掌与飞龙八步逼退张玉珍。张玉珍以威胁杀害红袍公、蓝髯客家小相要挟，芮玮承诺不用两位前辈的武功报仇。张玉珍趁机偷袭，芮玮险些中招。刘忠柱及时出现，以玉石像挡下暗器，但玉石像被射破十余洞。刘忠柱因妻子玉石像被毁而悲痛欲绝，追击张玉珍索要亡妻尸骨。张玉珍声称尸骨早已丢弃，刘忠柱精神失常，抱着残破玉石像紧追不舍。芮玮感叹痴情之苦，张玉珍此生难安。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好丫头？你说不报母仇因我救你一命之故，现在去杀你父亲又结父仇，父母双仇总该报了吧，到时倒要看你如何报仇，哼！\n难道你当真能杀得了我！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "给我站住！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的臭小子，装神弄鬼吓你老娘吗，把那脸上的捞什子拿下来，老娘知道你是谁了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "张玉珍，你还想杀人吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，我张玉珍喜杀人，红袍公、蓝髯客是我杀的，野儿的母亲也是我杀的，现在还要去杀她父亲。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "有我芮玮在，不容你再滥杀无辜！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "臭小子，高寿也不是你岳父，你拦我杀他，想讨野儿的欢心吗，可惜现在讨欢心已经迟了，那丫头出家为尼，这一生做定尼姑，总不成为你这臭小子再还俗吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，野儿既然抛弃了你，自个为尼，逍遥自在，却让你陷在感情深渊中痛苦，不如陪我宰掉高老匹夫，报复她对你无情，教她这一生永不能清静的修行。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "张玉珍，纳命来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "蓝髯客被我杀死，我还怕那套区区的化神掌法吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你不怕就上来试试！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的，你知道我为什么杀蓝髯客吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我知道！所以今天要以蓝老前辈的掌法，任老前辈的步法，两种绝学相加，杀他们的仇人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你知道就好，我说红袍公与蓝髯客死的真不值得，为了一个臭小子损命太划不来了，'红照一天高，蓝映四海深'啊！\n你们鼎鼎大名的快客，我张玉珍愿意杀你们吗？不！张玉珍念你们与我同处点苍山二十年之情，再怎么不愿杀你们，只怪你们传了臭小子的武功，应了当年的誓言，所创武功不如我便要横遭惨祸，但我张玉珍并不杀你们全家，可惜你俩死得真冤枉，不能说我杀你们，只怪那臭小子害了你们！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我本不愿杀你们家小，虽然我当年说过，再与我为敌，必杀满门，现在却不得了，因你们两人所创的武功又要与我为敌，只要我不死，当年的话一定要实行，你们俩位泉下有知，不要怪我张玉珍无情，怪传了臭小子的武功吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "张玉珍，你不要怪罪到红、蓝两位老前辈的家人身上，今天我替他们报仇不用他们所传的武功就是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不用他两人的武功，念在二十余年相处之情，不杀他们家小，可是我说臭小子，你不用他两人的武功是输定了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那不见得！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不信吗？你看是谁来了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "臭小子说话放屁吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那回不算，重新比过，决不再用！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "再比老娘不奉陪了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "活死人，又是你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "慧！慧！阿玉把你射伤，为夫决不再饶她！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "活死人，你发什么神经，对着石像哭个什么劲？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "大师伯，是我不好！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不怪你，不怪你！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "阿玉，为了师父，我一再饶恕你的行为，你若在点苍山从心向善，我决不与师父的女儿为敌，如今你不但盗走我妻子的尸骨，下山为恶，还毁坏我妻子的石像，说什么也不能饶你，师父，您老在天之灵，饶恕徒弟对你女儿不客气了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "且慢！活死人，我有话说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你还有什么话好说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "你说我盗你妻骨，那可是没法的事，我不盗你妻骨无法逼你下山，你不下山我这一辈子岂不要老死在点苍山？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "老死在点苍山有什么不好，点苍山风景绝佳，你能死在那里还不好吗？\n莫非你愿意闯荡江湖，终日过着凶险的生活？要知天外有天，人外有人，你以为武功高不怕为恶，哪知世上高人比比皆是，一旦遇到世外高手，你种种恶行必得恶报，与其惨死，不如在点苍山安分守己。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "世外高人毕竟是少的，我张玉珍可不怕谁，老死点苍山非我所愿，为尼终生更非我所愿，活死人，我为了自己不得不盗你妻骨，人不为己，天诛地灭，盗你妻骨之举，活死人，你却怪不得我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "不怪你怪谁，我与妻子终生厮守，永不分离，你活活拆散咱们，害得我孤苦寂寞，好不容易雕得一尊玉石像，以慰思念，如今石像又毁，阿玉，无论你怎么说，今天誓不与你罢休！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "活活拆散？我盗走一副死人骨头说得上活活拆散吗？\n活死人啊，我说你神经太不正常了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "胡说！我见妻骨如见她本人，在我想象中，你就等于拆散了咱们，你……你太狠心了，她在哪里？\n快还她来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "她是谁呀？可是那副死人骨头？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "快还她来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "我没兴趣为你保管尸骨，那副死人骨头早被丢得无影无踪，活死人，你断了痴想，莫再阴魂不散地缠着我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我妻子尸骨真的丢了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "还有假的吗？我可为了你好，否则让你留着，你这一辈子做定活死人了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慧！慧！我只剩你的玉像可资纪念了……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "张玉珍",
      "listener": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "text": "师兄，我看你无药可救，快将那石像丢掉，否则你又要入痴，终生懵懵无知，把那石像当做活人，你还有什么活头，小妹可为你好，再不要去想你那亡妻，振作起来吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "阿玉，你赔我妻子，今天赔不出来，誓要你命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_zhong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "刘忠柱",
      "listener": "char_zhang_yu_zhen",
      "text": "赔我妻子！赔我妻子……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 69,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    }
  ],
